450 REM
500 REM ---- DRAW ----
510 COLOR C
520 PLOT X, Y
530 REM
600 REM ---- DELAY AND CHECK SPACE ----
610 DELAY 14
620 IF PEEK(458809) = 1 THEN GOTO 700
630 GOTO 300
